-----------------------
Pre-requisite
-----------------------

Softwares:
Python - Version 2.7.14
PyCharm - download

Libraries: 
Logging
log

To run:
In PyCharm -
1. Go to Test_analyze_string - select run to get the output.

----------------------
Script Usage
----------------------

Syntax:  ./string_analyze.py <input_string>

input_string - contains the sentence for which longest word and length of longest string need to be find

Example:
string_analyze.py sumanth is great
Longest string = sumanth
Length of longest string = 7

string_analyze.py sumanth is great
Longest string = sumanth
Length of longest string = 7

